Company Overview of Reveal Mobile, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Reveal Mobile, Inc. operates a mobile audience platform for application publishers and developers. Its solutions include audience insights that provide audience data to create targeted campaigns based upon real-world and digital touch points; real-world and mobile behaviors; pre-built and custom personas; and rule programmatic ad buying. The company also provides a mobile SDK that allows developers to provide targeted audiences to their ad network based on a user's location, beacon interactions, and installed applications. Reveal Mobile, Inc. was formerly known as StepLeader, Inc. and changed its name to Reveal Mobile, Inc. in March 2015. The company was founded in 2004 and is based in Ralei...
Reveal Mobile, Inc. operates a mobile audience platform for application publishers and developers. Its solutions include audience insights that provide audience data to create targeted campaigns based upon real-world and digital touch points; real-world and mobile behaviors; pre-built and custom personas; and rule programmatic ad buying. The company also provides a mobile SDK that allows developers to provide targeted audiences to their ad network based on a user's location, beacon interactions, and installed applications. Reveal Mobile, Inc. was formerly known as StepLeader, Inc. and changed its name to Reveal Mobile, Inc. in March 2015. The company was founded in 2004 and is based in Raleigh, North Carolina. Reveal Mobile, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of CBC New Media Group, LLC.
